===Usage===
This template is for linking to the Film and TV Database page at the [[British Film Institute]] website. It should appear in the External links section.

<pre>* {{Bfidb title|id=|title=}}</pre>

The template has the following parameters:
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter
! Notes
|-
| '''id'''
| Programme id given after http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/. For example, the ''[[EastEnders]]'' entry is at http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/7133 and the id is 7133.
|-
| '''title'''
| Programme name, for the above example this would be EastEnders. The title is automatically formatted.
|-
| '''description'''
| Additional description
|}

